rows.label: qev092704_JNK0010
rows.name: Inform

rows.label: qev092704_SEL0020
rows.name: Explain that Grenada hired you.

rows.label: qev092704_MSG0030
rows.name: Grenada did? Ahh. Now it all makes sense.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092704_MSG0040
rows.name:
I bet I know who it was. Poor girl, 
she must've been worried sick.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092704_JNK0050
rows.name: Show Concern

rows.label: qev092704_SEL0060
rows.name: Ask if she's all right.

rows.label: qev092704_MSG0070
rows.name: Yeah. Not a single scratch on me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092704_MSG0080
rows.name:
If I'd gotten myself hurt,
I would never hear the end of it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092704_MSG0090
rows.name: In any case, I owe you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092704_MSG0100
rows.name:
My comms broke down out here.
I couldn't even call a ride home.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092704_MSG0110
rows.name: I'm lucky you showed up.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092704_MSG0120
rows.name: Oh, and...name's Liesel.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092704_MSG0125
rows.name: I'm a test pilot for Grenada Galactic.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092704_MSG0130
rows.name:
I'm grateful you bailed me out and all, but...
the Skell's the one that's in a bad way.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092704_MSG0140
rows.name:
It needs returning, and it won't make it
back unless I get it fixed up.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092704_MSG0150
rows.name:
It's highly classified, as you can imagine.
If I left it just sitting out here, they'd have my head.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092704_MSG0160
rows.name: Hmm...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092704_MSG0170
rows.name:
Hey, can I ask you a small favor?
It won't take too much of your time, I'm sure.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092704_MSG0180
rows.name:
Here's the deal: I need parts from around here
to patch this thing up and get it home.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092704_MSG0190
rows.name:
I'll send you what parts it needs.
I'd really appreciate the help.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092704_MSG0200
rows.name:
I'll stay here and get things repair-ready.
Thanks in advance. Best of luck.[ST:wait ]
